  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.10">
<l>ēḻai pētai yirāppakaṟaṉa</l>
<l>kēḻiloṇ kaṇṇanīr koṇṭāḷkiḷar</l>
<l>vāḻvaivēva vilaṅkaiceṟ ṟīrivaṇ</l>
<l>māḻainōk koṉṟum vāṭṭēṉmiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The simple girl, night [and] day she</l>
<l>holds water in her lustreless bright eyes.</l>
<l>You who subdued Laṅkā so that [its] shining life burned,</l>
<l>Don’t make fade any of her youthful looks!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
